      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Avoid when:"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " step N's correct action depends on step N-1's actual output (not just the fact that it ran). For example, if a web search might return zero results and the next step should change accordingly, use Plan-and-Execute or ReAct instead."
